    "The MBFC database is dynamic, and it does happen that the publisher label or metadata annotations change foot_2.",
    "Usually, this presents as a relatively minor change in political bias.",
    "During the data collection and processing period (Jan. 2017-Oct. 2024), we found 20 instances where the change was substantive (see Appendix B.5 Table B.6).",
